name: (1-of-1) GRONK Career Highlight Card
description: This NFT is limited to just 1 edition and will never be minted again. This NFT commemorates all of GRONK’s four championships. This card is a unique piece of memorabilia digitally hand signed by GRONK and is limited to just 1 edition. Illustrated by Black Madre, with creative vision given by GRONK.  In addition to winning the Career Highlight NFT card, the highest bidder of this auction will be awarded the opportunity to meet Rob Gronkowski and attend one of his football games & win VIP All-Access Tickets to the next Gronk Beach. (2x tickets / mutually agreeable game in 2021 season) **Must be holding this NFT on April 30, 2021 to redeem this offer**

name: GRONK Championship LI (Edition 1/87)
description: This NFT commemorates GRONK’s second championship - LI (2016-207). This card is a unique piece of memorabilia digitally hand signed by GRONK and is limited to just 87 editions sequentially numbered on the card. This card was hand drawn and illustrated by Black Madre, with creative vision given by GRONK.
